{"tid":710201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"葡萄牙場波真係一場假波既精彩示範","createTime":"2018-06-20T14:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T15:47:25.000Z","uid":87072,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8684cadfd8a149f109eb0475fe33a7c5cf78bc","tid":710201,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"踢完頭十幾分鐘好波之後，可以成場俾人禁住黎砌<br />\n俾人禁住黎砌無所謂，但可以癲到每下拎波都HOLD唔到十秒，<br />\n有位唔傳，傳就尻傳，接應果位就控到甩哂，<br />\n仲有全場基本上高空波即使俾葡萄牙球員頂到，都係頂俾摩洛哥球員再攻過<br />\n隔離有隊友唔頂，邊線唔頂，就係要頂俾對面球員腳下，守又HEA下HEA<br />\n臨完場條友仲痴線，可以HOLD住粒波等完場，佢就無人逼之下一腳飛機送番俾對面<br />\n如果你真係相信葡萄牙班友廢到咁都無計，但講緊唔少係歐洲頂級聯賽踢緊，會唔會真係全體發瘟，連波都唔識踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36878e8f960bb46c205516af1cb2b08751408073","tid":710201,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"拿3分 又唔俾人中讓球 咪要咁做"},{"pid":"7d7a2f5e3ac8945ea87cf3df7765d2caca5ba058","tid":710201,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36878e8f960bb46c205516af1cb2b08751408073","tid":710201,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"拿3分 又唔俾人中讓球 咪要咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"仲有黑哨，故意手球唔比牌"},{"pid":"5809e5a9c44aaea8e1534bedd41a21cfeac88785","tid":710201,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36878e8f960bb46c205516af1cb2b08751408073","tid":710201,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"拿3分 又唔俾人中讓球 咪要咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"真係，肯定呃左好多人中途買摩洛哥下一隊入球<br />\n<br />\n利申，我都差D買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41de5279f39236b56e03d1f3b7caf605cb521fe","tid":710201,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class